        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 7. Family Sesarmidae. A) Aratus pisonii (H. Milne Edwards, 1837) (CCDB 4890). B) Armases angustipes (Dana, 1852) (CCDB 5621). C) Armases rubripes (Rathbun, 1897) (CCDB 5653). D) Sesarma rectum Randall, 1840 (CCDB 5081). Animals from Brazil, São Paulo state: Cananéia (A), Ubatuba (B), Ilha Comprida (C, D). Sex: male (A, C), female (B, D). Scale bars (mm): A—12; B—11; C—8; D—20. Photographs by R.C. Buranelli." ;
